NK039(ti)015:0: rdo rje theg pa'i bstan bsrung chen mo re ma
NK039(ti)015:1: ti'i skong bshags kyi rim pa d+aak+ki gar mkhan brtse
NK039(ti)015:2: ba'i rgyang glu zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK039(ti)015:3: na mo ma h+aa gu ru rat+na ye /
NK039(ti)015:4: dur khrod brgyad sogs gnas yul zhing skyes kyi //
NK039(ti)015:5: tshogs kyi 'khor los bsgyur mdzad he ru ka /
NK039(ti)015:6: rnga yab gling gi bdag po gang de dang //
NK039(ti)015:7: dbyer med drin chen bla ma spyi bor rgyal //
NK039(ti)015:8: chos dbyings skye med rgyal yum gyis //
NK039(ti)015:9: rnam rol dza t+ai dbang phyug che //
NK039(ti)015:10: yang bzhengs 'dod khams dbang mo yis //
NK039(ti)015:11: thugs dam bskang ba'i rim pa bri //
NK039(ti)015:12: de la 'dir rgyal ba kun gyi yum mchog ma
NK039(ti)015:13: cig rdo rje re ma ti thugs dam bskang zhing
NK039(ti)015:14: dgyes pa bskyed pa'i phyir na //
NK039(ti)015:15: thabs 'di la nan tan du bya bar rig ste /
NK039(ti)015:16: de yang dur khrod la sogs pa 'jigs shing ya nga ba'i gnas su /
NK039(ti)015:17: rten gyi dkyil 'khor mngon par 'du bgyi par bsham pa'i mdun du 'bru tshom gyi dbus su /
NK039(ti)015:18: ma mo'i gtor ma brjid ldan sha khrag gis brgyan pa ngar mthing gi gdug dang bcas pa bshams /
NK039(ti)015:19: mtha' bskor du chu gnyis nyer spyod lnga dang sman rak+ta sogs sbreng tshar du bshams /
NK039(ti)015:20: gzhan yang nye mkho'i yo byad /
NK039(ti)015:24: ma mo 'bad pa'i spos sogs yo byad thams cad tshogs par bya'o //
NK039(ti)015:25: gnyis pa rang nyid lha yi rnal 'byor la gnas
NK039(ti)015:26: pa'i ngang nas cho ga'i las gzhung bsrangs nas bsnyen
NK039(ti)015:28: gsum pa thugs dam bskang ba'i rim pa dngos la rnam pa bzhi las /
NK039(ti)015:29: dang po bskang rdzas byin rlabs ni /
NK039(ti)015:30: stong pa'i ngang las sogs nas /
NK039(ti)015:31: ma mo chen mo rdo rje re ma ti la
NK039(ti)015:32: sogs pa bstan srung dam can rgya mtsho'i spyan la
NK039(ti)015:36: bar gyi gnas yo bskang rdzas bcas byin gyis rlabs so //
NK039(ti)015:37: gnyis pa thugs dam bskang ba'i rim pa rol mo dbyangs bcas /
NK039(ti)015:39: rdo rje srin mo chen mo re ma ti //
NK039(ti)015:40: rdo rje'i bka' sdod pho nya bran g.yog bcas //
NK039(ti)015:41: rdo rje pad+ma'i thugs dam gcer dgongs la //
NK039(ti)015:42: rdo rje'i tha tshig bzhin du da tshur byon //
NK039(ti)015:43: rnam mang mchod pa'i bye brag sna tshogs pa //
NK039(ti)015:44: nam mkha' mdzod kyi sgo 'phar yang phyes nas //
NK039(ti)015:45: sngags rgya ting 'dzin dag pa'i byin rlabs pa //
NK039(ti)015:46: ma khyed thugs dam bskang ba'i dpyid du spro //
NK039(ti)015:47: gsar rnying thod rtsegs glad zhag zhal bas mdzes //
NK039(ti)015:48: lcang lo'i kha bad rgyu ma'i dra phyed 'phyong //
NK039(ti)015:49: dbugs bral rgyal mtshan zhing gi bla re dang //
NK039(ti)015:50: rngam brjid rol pa drag pa'i pho brang 'dis //
NK039(ti)015:51: re ti bran g.yog 'khor bcas thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)015:52: lcang lor bcas pa'i b+han+dza'i snod yang por //
NK039(ti)015:53: nang gsang phyi yi dgra bgegs bsgral ba yi //
NK039(ti)015:54: sha ri khrag mtsho rus pa'i gram khrod 'khrigs //
NK039(ti)015:55: rmad byung gtor ma rgyan ldan dam pa 'dis //
NK039(ti)015:56: 'dod khams dbang phyug 'khor bcas thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)015:57: rtsa brgyad yan lag stong sbyar ra sa yan //
NK039(ti)015:58: dmar chen rak+ta'i rgya mtsho sbu 'phreng 'khrigs //
NK039(ti)015:59: 'bru bcud 'chi med bdud rtsi'i skyems sogs kyis //
NK039(ti)015:60: re ti bran g.yog 'khor bcas gzugs reg sgra snyan dri zhim ro bda' dang //
NK039(ti)015:61: ta na ga na sbyor sgrol gsang mchod che //
NK039(ti)015:62: gsang rten tsit+ta shing lo rlung khyer sogs //
NK039(ti)015:63: phyi nang gsang ba'i rten rdzas sna tshogs kyis //
NK039(ti)015:64: 'dod khams dbang phyug 'khor bcas dbang po'i me tog tshil gsur dud sprin 'khrigs //
NK039(ti)015:65: rkang chen sgron me mkhris sna'i dri yi khyab //
NK039(ti)015:66: sha rul zhal zas rkang gling thod rnga sogs //
NK039(ti)015:67: mchod pa'i bye brag rnam mang rgya chen pos //
NK039(ti)015:68: re ti bran g.yog 'khor bcas rnam bkra dar gyi rgyan ldan rta nag dang //
NK039(ti)015:69: mi sdug rwa rtse g.yo ba'i zhol chen tshogs //
NK039(ti)015:70: 'jam legs spu sdug yid 'ong lug nag dang //
NK039(ti)015:71: dgra bgegs glad pa 'gem pa'i bya tshogs kyis //
NK039(ti)015:72: 'dod khams dbang phyug 'khor bcas 'jigs rung mche gtsigs rngams pa'i mi nag dang //
NK039(ti)015:73: mon mo nag mo dgra la dug nad 'debs //
NK039(ti)015:74: dam nyams srog 'phrog dam dang gcan spyang dang //
NK039(ti)015:75: dar gyi cod pan g.yo ba'i khyi nag 'dis //
NK039(ti)015:76: re ti bran g.yog long ka'i yul gyi mgrin bzang dmar gwa la //
NK039(ti)015:77: srin thod dga' dang lpags pas rab g.yogs shing //
NK039(ti)015:78: gong smed srab mthur gdug pa'i sbrul gyis brgyan //
NK039(ti)015:79: 'dzam gling yud kyis bskor ba'i zhen pa 'dis //
NK039(ti)015:80: 'dod khams dbang phyug 'khor bcas mi lpags gos dang re lde'i smad g.yog dang //
NK039(ti)015:81: rma bya'i gdug la nyi ma zla bas brgyan //
NK039(ti)015:82: rlung nag 'tshubs gur nad rdzing khrag zhag mtsho //
NK039(ti)015:83: sra rno go mtshon spyan gzigs rnam mang 'dis //
NK039(ti)015:84: re ti bran g.yog 'khor ral gri 'bar ba ne le'i rkyal bu dang //
NK039(ti)015:85: nad kyi rkyal pa tshon gyi gru gu dang //
NK039(ti)015:86: bdud kyi khram shing shwa d+hil dkar nag sogs //
NK039(ti)015:87: mgo phreng byug pa dur khrod rgyan rnams kyis //
NK039(ti)015:88: 'dod khams dbang phyug 'khor bcas phyag rgya lnga dang snyan rgyan seng ge sbrul //
NK039(ti)015:89: mda' dar me long dung shwos rgyan pa dang //
NK039(ti)015:90: ri gling gser gyi ri bdun rol mtsho bdun //
NK039(ti)015:91: nyi ma zla ba lha ma'i dpal 'byor rnams //
NK039(ti)015:92: re ti bran g.yog gzhan yang 'khor bcas srid pa'i dpal 'byor tshogs //
NK039(ti)015:93: dngos su 'byor bshams yid kyi legs sprul nas //
NK039(ti)015:94: rgyal por 'os pa bdun dang rin chen brgyad //
NK039(ti)015:95: kun bzang mchod sprin rab 'byams dpag med 'dis //
NK039(ti)015:96: 'dod khams dbang phyug chos dbyings bzang mo e ka dza ti ma //
NK039(ti)015:97: gdug pa 'dul phyir 'dod khams dbang phyug gi //
NK039(ti)015:98: skur bzhengs ye shes me mo lhun gyis grub //
NK039(ti)015:99: yid chos gsol 'debs bla med rten mchog 'dis //
NK039(ti)015:100: re ti bran g.yog 'khor bcas thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)015:101: gsum pa bshags pa bya ba ni sgo gsum gnong 'gyod dang bcas pas /
NK039(ti)015:103: dbyings kyi rgyal mo ye shes rol pa'i rtsal //
NK039(ti)015:104: ma mo chen mo dam ldan re ma t+ai //
NK039(ti)015:105: 'khor tshogs sde dang bcas pa ma lus pa //
NK039(ti)015:106: thugs rje'i bdag la gsan cing dgongs su gsol //
NK039(ti)015:107: bdag cag mi shes rmongs 'khrul le lo yis //
NK039(ti)015:108: slob dpon smod dang gsang sngags bzlas brjod g.yel //
NK039(ti)015:109: gsang bcu bsgrag cing man ngag 'chal bar spyod //
NK039(ti)015:110: rtsa ba'i dam las 'gal ba mthol lo bshags //
NK039(ti)015:111: mi spang lnga dang dang len spyod bya lnga //
NK039(ti)015:112: shes bya lnga dang bsgrub bya lnga la sogs //
NK039(ti)015:113: rtsa ba yan lag dam tshig nyams pa rnams //
NK039(ti)015:114: rang gnang 'gyod pa chen pos bshags par bgyi //
NK039(ti)015:115: thugs rje'i gter gyur lha mo khyod nyid kyis //
NK039(ti)015:116: bdag cag dpon slob yon chod 'khor bcas rnams //
NK039(ti)015:117: g.yel med rtag tu srung zhing skyabs pa la //
NK039(ti)015:118: gtang rag dus su ma mthong mthol lo bshags //
NK039(ti)015:119: bstan dang bstan 'dzin yongs la gnod pa yi //
NK039(ti)015:120: dam nyams dgra bgegs sdig can de dag la //
NK039(ti)015:121: dbang bskur byin rlabs byams kyis skyong ba sogs //
NK039(ti)015:122: khyod kyi thugs dam 'gal nyams mthol lo bshags //
NK039(ti)015:123: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod rdzas rten rdzas la //
NK039(ti)015:124: rgyu chung phud nyams 'bag rtsog dri mas gos //
NK039(ti)015:125: dus kyi mchod gtor chags shing nyams pa sogs //
NK039(ti)015:126: sgo gsum gnang 'gyod drag po'i bshags par bgyi //
NK039(ti)015:127: khyod ni dam tshig gnyen la rtag gnas shing //
NK039(ti)015:128: bdag gi nyams chag phra mo byung srid na //
NK039(ti)015:129: mi dmigs chos nyid klong du bzod bzhes nas //
NK039(ti)015:130: 'gyur med dag cing tshang par stsal du gsol //
NK039(ti)015:131: ces yig brgya brjod cing dgos pa can la skabs
NK039(ti)015:132: su srung ma dang khon bcug bshags pa ni gzhan
NK039(ti)015:133: du shes so // bzhi pa 'phrin las bcol ba ni /
NK039(ti)015:135: de ltar dgyes mchod nyams chag bshags pa'i mthus //
NK039(ti)015:136: khyod kyi mthu stobs nyi ma bye ba'i gzis //
NK039(ti)015:137: phas rgol ku mu ta tshal zum byas nas //
NK039(ti)015:138: bdag sogs bstan 'dzin pad tshal rgyas par mdzod //
NK039(ti)015:139: bdag cag dpon slob rgyu 'khor bcas la //
NK039(ti)015:140: nad mug mtshon 'khrugs dal yams bar chad bdud //
NK039(ti)015:141: bshad sgrub sde dgon 'jigs pa'i sbyor rtsub kun //
NK039(ti)015:142: ma lus zhi zhing tshe bsod ye shes stobs //
NK039(ti)015:143: thos bsam bsgom pa'i yon tan rgyas par mdzod //
NK039(ti)015:144: snang srid 'khor 'das rlung sems snang ba kun //
NK039(ti)015:145: dbang du 'dus shing bdud bzhi'i nyer tshe'i dgra //
NK039(ti)015:146: ma lus drag po brlag pa'i phrin las mdzod //
NK039(ti)015:147: gnas skabs mi mthun las rgyal grib bzhin 'grogs //
NK039(ti)015:148: mthur thug zag bral 'gyur med thig le'i gzhir //
NK039(ti)015:149: mngon gyur gdod ma'i dpal mchog dang po nyid //
NK039(ti)015:150: he ru ka dpal myur du 'grub par shog /
NK039(ti)015:151: ces phrin las bcol ba drag tu bya'o //
NK039(ti)015:152: de ltar rdo rje'i bstan skyong chen mo d+ae wa
NK039(ti)015:153: ti dgyes bskyed bskong bshags kyi rim pa d+aak+ki gar
NK039(ti)015:154: mkhan brtse ba'i rgyang glu zhes bya ba 'adi'ang bstan
NK039(ti)015:155: bsrung chen mo dgyes pa'i mtshan ma byung bar brten
NK039(ti)015:156: te / chos rje kahthoga pa'i bran gyi tha shal
NK039(ti)015:157: gsang chen rdo rje theg pa'i bstan pa la mos
NK039(ti)015:158: pa lam byed kyi sprul ming rmongs btul ba la
NK039(ti)015:159: 'gyur med kun bzang nges don dbang po zhes pa'i
NK039(ti)015:160: kahthoga rdo rje'i gdan gyis gtsug lag khang gis mgon
NK039(ti)015:161: khang rab 'jigs rtsub 'gyur tshal du rdo rje gzhon
NK039(ti)015:162: nu'i bsnyen bsgrub kyis mthun seng zhig tu 'phral byung
